versity%20of%20Birmingham's%20Law%20School%2C%20has%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20affect%20not%20just%20legal%20issues%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20very%20important%20social%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20deeply%20philosophical%20issues%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbinja%2C%20who%20specializes%20in%20digital%20rights%20and%20post-mortem%20privacy%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22307f42e1-1211-4856-a9e8-9e38c35a1eae%5C%22%3EGetting%20into%20the%20business%20of%20grief%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20has%20thought%20about%20managing%20digital%20legacies%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Facebook%20launched%20tools%20that%20let%20people%20designate%20a%20%26quot%3Blegacy%20contact%26quot%3B%20to%20manage%20their%20accounts%20if%20they%20died.%20And%20back%20in%20the%20company's%20metaverse%20days%2C%20in%20a%202023%20interview%20with%20podcaster%20Lex%20Fridman%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20discussed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzuckerberg-on-using-metaverse-to-bring-back-the-dead-virtually-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evirtual%20avatars%20for%20deceased%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20has%20lost%20a%20loved%20one%20and%20is%20grieving%2C%20there%20may%20be%20ways%20in%20which%20being%20able%20to%20interact%20or%20relive%20certain%20memories%20could%20be%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20names%20for%20this%20broader%20category%20of%20tech%20%E2%80%94%20death%20bots%2C%20ghost%20bots%2C%20grief%20tech%20%E2%80%94%20that%20are%20aiming%20to%20help%20people%20face%20the%20loss%20of%20loved%20ones%20with%20eternally%20memorialized%20digital%20versions%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20startups%20have%20launched%20around%20this%20premise%2C%20and%20many%20have%20emerged%20from%20founders'%20own%20experiences%20with%20grief.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feternime-and-replika-giving-life-to-the-dead-with-new-technology-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReplika%2C%20an%20AI%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20startup%2C%20was%20founded%20in%202015%20by%20Eugenia%20Kuyda%20after%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20friend.%20Then%20there's%20You%2C%20Only%20Virtual%20(YOV)%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202020%20by%20Justin%20Harrison%20when%20his%20mother%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20in%20the%20tech%20world%20has%20been%20thinking%20about%20this%20for%20a%20while%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20started%20having%20breaks%20in%20generative%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-patents-a-chatbot-to-imitate-real-people-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20patented%20an%20AI%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20simulate%20a%20deceased%20person%20(as%20well%20as%20fictional%20characters%20or%20celebrities).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20patent%20signals%20that%20the%20technology%20category%20is%20moving%20more%20into%20the%20mainstream%2C%20Harbinja%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarrison%20isn't%20surprised%20to%20see%20bigger%20tech%20companies%20dipping%20their%20toes%20in%20the%20space%2C%20and%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20sign%20that%20people%20are%20beginning%20to%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20more%20comfortable%20with%20doing%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20only%20improve%20on%20what%20we%20offer%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrison%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20resources%20for%20grieving%20are%20%26quot%3Bhorrible%26quot%3B%20to%20begin%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20have%20a%20moral%20obligation%2C%20if%20we%20have%20the%20potential%2C%20to%20do%20more%20for%20those%20folks%20than%20we%20should%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%2C%20death%2C%20and%20grief%20are%20not%20easy%20topics%20to%20digest%2C%20however.%20The%20intersection%20of%20all%20three%20is%20a%20potent%20brew%20of%20taboos%20ripe%20for%20a%20philosophical%20debate%20on%20ethics%2C%20digital%20rights%2C%20and%20privacy%20for%20any%20dinner%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b60e8ee-cbdd-4ad0-991b-72de5e7cbfee%5C%22%3E'Let%20the%20dead%20be%20dead'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20has%20more%20than%20helping%20people%20process%20grief%20as%20an%20incentive%20to%20pursue%20the%20tech%20it%20lays%20out%20in%20its%20patent%2C%20especially%20for%20accounts%20taking%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20engagement%2C%20more%20content%2C%20more%20data%20%E2%80%94%20more%20data%20for%20the%20current%20and%20the%20future%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbinja%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20the%20business%20incentive%20for%20that.%20I'm%20just%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20they%20would%2C%20when%2C%20and%20if%20they%20will%20implement%20this%20innovation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20a%20product%20like%20this%20is%20rolled%20out%2C%20different%20questions%20could%20come%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20would%20this%20apply%20across%20all%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta's%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Would%20it%20understand%20the%20nuance%20of%20your%20WhatsApp%20presence%20vs.%20the%20candor%20you%20have%20in%20the%20Instagram%20comment%20section%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Davis%2C%20a%20sociology%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%2C%20said%20he%20was%20concerned%20with%20the%20impact%20that%20tools%20like%20a%20Meta%20bot%20could%20have%20on%20how%20humans%20experience%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20tasks%20of%20grief%20is%20to%20face%20the%20actual%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20the%20dead%20be%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20of%20bringing%20them%20back%2C%20but%20you're%20not%20really%20doing%20that%2C%20but%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20that.%20That's%20the%20confusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asbradley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esbradley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20sydneykbradley.123.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-granted-patent-for-ai-llm-bot-dead-paused-accounts-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1770834520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698cb3e0a645d1188189232d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-granted-patent-for-ai-llm-bot-dead-paused-accounts-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20was%20recently%20granted%20a%20patent%20for%20tech%20to%20keep%20your%20social%20media%20accounts%20running%20using%20AI%20if%20you%20take%20a%20break%20or%20die.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbradley%40insider.com%20(Sydney%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A72%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-granted-patent-for-ai-llm-bot-dead-paused-accounts-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Powerful%20cyclone%20kills%20at%20least%2031